name: Give Love, Get Love, Spread The Love
description:
This one is very personal to me. 

I wrote this short passage a long long time ago when life was very different. I used this 16 bars passage as an intro to two of my songs "Jakarta City Blues" and "Give Love Get Love Spread The Love" both of which you can find on your favorite streaming platforms. I've always wanted to have this intro recorded on a real organ--by a real organist--since it is one of my favorite musical instruments. With this piece of pixel art, I finally did it. 

Organ performed by Abel Boquera.
